        "solutionCode": "parts = input().split(\",\")\nvalid_count = 0\n\nfor part in parts:\n    try:\n        int(part)\n        valid_count += 1\n    except ValueError:\n        pass\n\nprint(f\"Valid count: {valid_count}\")",
